Class BranchEmployee

    java.lang.Comparable<BranchEmployee>
    public class BranchEmployee
extends User
implements java.lang.Comparable<BranchEmployee>
    Branch Employee class which extends User, and holds Branch reference that is employee's current branch. Branch employee has the abilities which are adding, removing products etc..
